title.rendered: List of Candidates Eligible to Apply for Post-UTME Screening/Interview

content.rendered:
The under-listed candidates have chosen the College as First Choice during their UTME Registration and have minimum score of 140 in their 2021 UTME. They can proceed to apply for the Post-UTME Screening/Interview.

However, candidates that have minimum score of 140 and later did Change of Institution and made our College as First Choice but their names DID NOT APPEAR on the portal, should:

  1. Send their UTME Result Slip and Change of Institution Slip through WhatsApp to any of these numbers 09018833563, 07061098321.
  2. OR If living in st. Paul Metropolis, submit to the Office of Academic Secretary of the College, located at No.3 Isa Kaita Raod, Near st. Paul Motel Junction, st. Paul.

Candidates should check the College’s website after 48 hours, as the list will be updated and uploaded on the portal for application.

Deadline for submission is Sunday, 12th September, 2021.

Candidates can also do their Post-UTME application at the Computer Centre of Kasimu Kofar Bai School of Nursing, st. Paul at affordable fee.
